<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُوْلِي بَاسٍ}</span> ... ذَوِي شَجَاعَةٍ وَقُوَّةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
